35
00:02:28,716 --> 00:02:31,422
[crying]

36
00:02:31,452 --> 00:02:33,757
My name is Grace

37
00:02:33,787 --> 00:02:37,561
and this is my beautiful life.

38
00:02:37,591 --> 00:02:40,527
[police siren wailing]

39
