to Mr. Matthew Clifton,

154
00:11:27,821 --> 00:11:29,259
our teacher's aide.

155
00:11:29,289 --> 00:11:33,159
Now, please fill out
the information sheets.

156
00:11:33,827 --> 00:11:38,201
And remember,
this is a very important year.

157
00:11:38,231 --> 00:11:41,138
So please work hard.

158
00:11:41,168 --> 00:11:42,472
